{"tid":937004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄搏擊冠軍美少女浴室內觸電身亡 兇手是iPhone","createTime":"2018-12-11T08:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T13:57:25.000Z","uid":212399,"like":50,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"abdf625b619b573cf953641f12366ad23dbec1f3","tid":937004,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"近日俄羅斯一名15歲的搏擊冠軍在家中身亡，導致她喪命的罪魁禍首正是她的手機。報導指出因為手機掉到浴缸中，這名少女當場觸電身亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/11/99/5647012.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F11%2F99%2F5647012.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=7714bfcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年僅15歲的伊琳娜不僅外貌出眾，還是俄羅斯的搏擊冠軍。<br />\n俄羅斯伊爾庫茨克州的15歲搏擊冠軍伊琳娜&middot;雷布尼科娃(Irina Rybnikova)，相當擅長一種源自古希臘的「無規則」拳擊和摔角搏擊，她於兩個月前剛贏得俄羅斯的冠軍賽並獲選為國家代表隊的一員，她的朋友說成為世界冠軍是她的夢想。日前伊琳娜帶著充電中的iPhone一起進入浴室，不久後被發現喪命其中。眾人惋惜這名搏擊新星還來不及發光發熱時，即因不幸的意外而喪失性命。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/11/99/5647067.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F11%2F99%2F5647067.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=6ca0d8ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成為世界冠軍曾是伊琳娜的夢想，可惜如今已無法朝夢想前進。<br />\n據「鏡報」報導，伊爾庫茨克州立大學的無線電研究主任表示水是電流的絕佳導體，因此手機一掉到水裡就會立刻造成了短路，「假如手機不是正在充電中，也許還有機會避免這場悲劇」。俄羅斯的安全官也曾對在浴室中使用充電的手機提出警告，認為這種行為非常危險。<br />\n伊琳娜出眾的外貌、體育上優異的表現以及和善的性格為她贏得了好人緣，今年八月她剛成為自己姪女的教母，不僅是家人間的重要支柱，也倍受朋友同學的喜愛。如今她不幸因意外身亡，讓家人朋友們都大受打擊。<br />\n網路上有酸民對這起意外作出無情的嘲弄，認為搏擊冠軍居然死在浴室裡「真是史上最窩囊死法」。這種說法也引起伊琳娜朋友的氣憤回應，認為做出這種評論的人是「非常不道德的冷血動物」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NuZsAQC7rKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNuZsAQC7rKo&d=VsC9aI3sO9H7xHrCPdzk6F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9dcc385d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NuZsAQC7rKo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6812/3530426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6812%2F3530426&d=VsC9aI3sO9H7xHrCPdzk6F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=48d9dece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6812/3530426</a>"},{"pid":"fbdfe1cdb0cfe160de70a89f22596464b73e41f5","tid":937004,"uid":60164,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bb18d01f15d21b44b462278414346de48eaa56","tid":937004,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba219ff3f1817aa7bd8fc496134545c28f78fbe","tid":937004,"uid":30966,"like":167,"dislike":0,"score":167,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"差緊電跌落水"},{"pid":"254835525260ff85d1505094b1a38a9a76cdee63","tid":937004,"uid":198583,"like":10,"dislike":257,"score":-247,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:21:28.000Z","msg":"華為吾會咁樣囉<br />\n<br />\n明顯美帝背後做事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBte 可吾可以比我屌左先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7232f6745df99507ae515944106a163d17b6b0","tid":937004,"uid":113073,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"就黎連電線之間都要加fuse"},{"pid":"d18c448788e17bdeb5a0ceb4038c862f9dd68b6c","tid":937004,"uid":130320,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"Fake news is so 唔識講"},{"pid":"ebc584c7f4cef454d8ba10c7ffa4f5f0ae89469c","tid":937004,"uid":54486,"like":54,"dislike":7,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:26:10.000Z","msg":"唔明，經過火牛出usb先5v，都電得死？"},{"pid":"469810b5883fc92875dde3dd08469fc689e0d301","tid":937004,"uid":49918,"like":33,"dislike":14,"score":19